      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's good to hear, but I'm looking at some of the raw telemetry from the player logs on Match 5, and there's a weird spike in frame timing right during the final engagement. It looks like the winning player might have had an advantage due to a frame-rate jump. Are you absolutely certain we don't need to flag this? I'd hate for someone to dig into the logs later and think we were hiding something.",
